{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 300,
      "y": -140,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "# LoreAI v2 — Pipeline Architecture\n> Strategy-role grouping with timing & key data flows"
    },

    {
      "id": "signal-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -60,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 740,
      "label": "🔵 Signal Engine",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## A — News Collection\n**⏰ 4:00 AM SGT** Mon–Fri\n\n`collect-news.ts`\n7 source tiers · ~350 items/day\nRSS · Twitter · GitHub · HF · HN · Reddit · Blogs\n→ `news_items` table (SQLite)"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-a2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 280,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## A2 — Entity Extraction\n**⏰ 6:30 AM SGT**\n\n`extract-entities.ts` · Claude Sonnet 4.6\nExtracts company/model/tech/framework entities\n→ `topic_clusters` + `keywords` tables\n+ Brave expansion for new topics"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-h",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## H — GSC Export\n**Manual / Cron**\n\n`gsc-export.ts`\nGoogle Search Console API → 7-day window\n→ `data/gsc-exports/latest.csv`"
    },

    {
      "id": "planner-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 560,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 740,
      "label": "🟡 Graph Planner",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 600,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 340,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## E — Cluster Discovery\n**Manual / Cron**\n\n`planner.ts` + `lib/discover.ts`\n6-stage candidate discovery:\n\n1. SERP Demand (Serper.dev · 7 queries)\n2. Exa Semantic Gap (findSimilar)\n3. Competitor Audit (Exa/Brave + LLM)\n4. News Signals (14-day scan + LLM)\n5. GSC Import (unmatched queries)\n6. Multi-signal Scoring (0–100)\n\n→ `flagship-clusters/{slug}.json`\n+ promote / dismiss workflow"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-j",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 600,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## J — Weekly Strategy\n**Cron / Manual**\n\n`generate-seo.ts --weekly-strategy`\n\nGap analysis: clusters × existing content\nBrave demand validation (top 10 topics)\n→ Priority-scored content plan\n→ `data/content-plan/{week}.json`"
    },

    {
      "id": "gen-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 1160,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 1060,
      "label": "🟢 Asset Generation",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1200,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## B — Newsletter\n**⏰ 5:00 AM SGT** Mon–Fri\n\n`write-newsletter.ts`\n3-tier agent filter → JSON outline\nEN (Opus) + ZH (3-tier fallback)\nBlog seed extraction (3-signal score)\nEmail HTML generation\n→ newsletters · seeds · filtered-items · email"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1200,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## C — Blog Generation\n**⏰ 7:00 AM SGT** Mon–Fri\n\n`write-blog.ts`\nTop 2–3 seeds · source URL fetch\nEN + ZH via Claude Opus\nSEO entity extraction → keywords"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1200,
      "y": 540,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## D — SEO Daily\n**⏰ 9:00 AM SGT**\n\n`generate-seo.ts`\nGap analysis: keywords × content existence\nMax 8 pages/run · EN + ZH\n\nTypes: Glossary · FAQ · Compare · Topic Hub\n→ `content/{type}/{lang}/{slug}.md`"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1200,
      "y": 800,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## F — Cluster Generation\n**Manual / Cron**\n\n`generate-seo.ts --cluster=<SLUG>`\nSource resolution: curated → Exa → Brave\nCornerstone (2000–4000 tokens)\n+ Compare/FAQ/Glossary (max 8/run)\n→ Update cluster JSON status"
    },

    {
      "id": "refresh-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -60,
      "y": 820,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 380,
      "label": "🟡 Refresh Engine",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-g",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 880,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## G — Refresh Detection & Execution\n**Manual**\n\n**Detection** `--refresh-check`:\nFreshness signals → page mapping\nLLM staleness check → severity flags\n\n**Execution** `--refresh`:\nRe-generate with fresh sources\nEN + ZH independently\nPreserves internal links"
    },

    {
      "id": "dist-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 560,
      "y": 820,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 380,
      "label": "🟣 Distribution Engine",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-i",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 600,
      "y": 880,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "## I — Weekly Digest\n**⏰ Saturday 5:00 AM SGT**\n\n`write-weekly.ts`\n5 top stories + video posts + cluster updates\nEN + ZH (3-tier model fallback)"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-l",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 600,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 100,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "## L — Distribution\n**L1** `send-newsletter.ts` → Email to subscribers\n**L2** Git push → Vercel SSG → loreai.dev"
    },

    {
      "id": "mon-group",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 1160,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 280,
      "label": "⚪ Monitoring Layer (cross-cutting)"
    },
    {
      "id": "pipe-k",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1200,
      "y": 1200,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "## K — Monitoring & Reporting\n\n**K1** `cluster-health.ts` — Completeness · links · GSC\n**K2** `generate-review.ts` — Daily validation dashboard\n**K3** `validate-pipeline.ts` — Pre-commit quality gate"
    },

    {
      "id": "timeline",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 150,
      "y": 1500,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 360,
      "text": "## Daily Timeline (SGT, Mon–Fri)\n\n```\n04:00  A  — collect-news         ~350 items → news_items\n05:00  B  — write-newsletter     EN + ZH newsletters + seeds + email\n06:30  A2 — extract-entities     Entities → topic_clusters + keywords\n07:00  C  — write-blog           2-3 blog posts (EN + ZH)\n09:00  D  — generate-seo         Up to 8 SEO pages (EN + ZH)\n  →    L  — git push             Vercel SSG rebuild → loreai.dev\n\nSat    I  — write-weekly         Weekly digest (EN + ZH)\n\nAd-hoc E/F/G/H/J/K              Discovery · cluster gen · refresh · monitoring\n```"
    },

    {
      "id": "stores",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 150,
      "y": 1920,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 280,
      "text": "## Data Stores\n\n**SQLite Tables**: `news_items` · `topic_clusters` · `keywords` · `content` · `content_sources` · `subscribers`\n\n**File Stores**:\n- `data/blog-seeds/{DATE}.json` — B → C\n- `data/filtered-items/{DATE}.json` — B → I, K\n- `data/flagship-clusters/{slug}.json` — E ↔ F ↔ G, K\n- `data/gsc-exports/latest.csv` — H → E, K\n- `data/content-plan/{week}.json` — J → manual\n- `content/{newsletters,blog,glossary,faq,compare,topics}/` — All generators → L (Vercel)"
    }
  ],
